description.en:
CumRocket (CUMMIES) is a deflationary token that will be used for tipping and messaging content creators on our adult content platforms. This includes an 18+ NFT marketplace as well as a private NSFW content subscription feed. 5% tax occurs on every transaction (2.5% burn, 2.5% redistribution).

The NFT Marketplace is set to be released by the end of April, with some well-known creators lined up for launch! Our other platform where creators can charge a monthly or yearly fee in exchange for private content will be launched in Q3.

Using CUMMIES as the currency on our NSFW platforms encourages more transactions. This means holders will be able to reap the 5% tax rewards a whole lot more often!
Also, since the creators' main wage doesn't depend on it, they are more likely to HOLD and watch their CUMMIES grow!
